data.description:
Nice Clean 3 Bedroom, 1 Full Bath Ranch Featuring Newer Recessed Lighting in Living Room, Eat-In Kitchen Area and Hallway. Kitchen Features Newer Kitchen Cabinetry with Granite Countertops and Recessed Sink with Touch Faucet! Kitchen is FULLY Applianced with Range/Oven, Microwave, Refrigerator & Garbage Disposal. Roof 2 Years Old. Nice level totally fenced in back Yard with Gazebo and 16' above ground round swimming pool, 52" deep with pump & ladder that will stay (Owners store it in the winter). Main Electric Service updated in 2023.

A Great affordable home with EVERYTHING on one floor!
